and see config/config.json and insert:

  FROM:
  "domain": {
    "base_domain": "localhost",
    "public_port": 48763
  },
  TO:
  "domain": {
    "base_domain": "fluxer.dev",
    "public_port": 48763,
    "public_scheme": "https"
  },

mkdir certs
please create a certs/fluxer.conf with:
``[req]                                                                                                                                                                                   
default_bits = 4096                                                                                                                                                                     
prompt = no                                                                                                                                                                             
default_md = sha256                                                                                                                                                                     
req_extensions = req_ext                                                                                                                                                                
distinguished_name = dn                                                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                                        
[dn]                                                                                                                                                                                    
CN = fluxer.dev                                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                        
[req_ext]                                                                                                                                                                               
subjectAltName = @alt_names                                                                                                                                                             
                                                                                                                                                                                        
[alt_names]                                                                                                                                                                             
DNS.1 = fluxer.dev                                                                                                                                                                      
DNS.2 = localhost                                                                                                                                                                       
IP.1 = 127.0.0.1                                                                                                                                                                        
IP.2 = <<PLEASE REPLACE HERE YOUR PUBLIC IP BEFORE YOU SAVE THIS CONFIGURATION!!!>>``


cd ~/fluxer/certs
openssl req -x509 -newkey rsa:4096 -keyout fluxer.key -out fluxer.crt -days 365 -nodes -config fluxer.conf
ls -la ~/fluxer/certs

